(1)ifconfig check IP addr and mac la:st 6 number
(2)ping 135.57.46.122,make sure is ok
(3) yum install *.rpm
(4) fix four pcnt* and four psvr*

vi /etc/paratera/pcnt.conf

/* The cluster attributes. */
cluster {
  name = "C内网ip mac地址后六位"    如果mac地址后六位为111111  那么这里写C111111
  owner = "C内网ip mac地址后六位"   如果mac地址后六位为111111  那么这里写C111111
  latlong = "N40.02 E116.18"
  url = "http://www.paratera.com"
}


/* Back-end server IP address and the udp_send_channel port number */
udp_send_channel {
  host = 内网ip
  port = 10089
}
 and other file is same .

(5) fix four psvr*

vi /etc/paratera/pcnt.conf

/* The cluster attributes. */
cluster {
  name = "C内网ip mac地址后六位"    如果mac地址后六位为111111  那么这里写C111111
  owner = "C内网ip mac地址后六位"   如果mac地址后六位为111111  那么这里写C111111
  latlong = "N40.02 E116.18"
  url = "http://www.paratera.com"
}


/* Back-end server IP address and the udp_send_channel port number */
udp_send_channel {
  host = 内网ip
  port = 10089
}

 and other file is same .


(6)the server node :

service paramon-svr start
service paramon start

(7)

vi /opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/etc/plrtcli.conf
SendQueName  = C内网ip mac地址后六位
HostName     = 123.57.46.122
ParaSvrIP    = 本机外网ip 

(8)cd /opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8
. setp_paramon_cli ( or source setp_paramon_cli )
/opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/start.sh

(9)把/opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/start.sh添加到/etc/profile (开机启动)

(10)for other node , execute the following command :

pdsh shenma[101-161]  pcnt*  /etc/paratera 

service paramon start 


other command :

telnet 127.0.0.1 10091 |grep 'HOST NAME'

telnet 127.0.0.1 10091 

telnet 127.0.0.1 10091 |grep CLUSTER

ps aux |grep pl_

sysctl -a|grep kernel.shm

ll -h /opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/log/*

nc 202.127.204.22 10091

ps -aux|grep psvr 

/opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/start.sh

/opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/stop.sh

chkconfig paramon-svr on

然后把/opt/paratera/PARAMONCLI8/start.sh添加到/etc/profile (开机启动)  确保您的数据能够联通到我们公司 这样才会出周报

功能集中在查看选项卡下面

如果每个机器有ib卡 那么需要把/etc/paratera/utils.conf 里面第二行ib信息收集从off 改成on

每个有ib的机器都要改 改完了 还需要 service paramon restart

如果想看作业信息 那么需要更改登陆节点的/etc/paratera/utils.conf  里面有作业调度的模版 照着更改就行

然后service paramon restart

paramon会根据pcnt的信息把数据传给paramon-svr的节点，
然后paramon-svr 根据psvr信息显示数据


xdsh shenma5 yum install -y /scratch/pkg/software/paramon-pro-5.0.0-956.centos6.x86_64.rpm



xdcp shenma[1-6] ~/pcnt*   /etc/paratera/
xdcp shenma[1-6]  utils.conf  /etc/paratera/

xdsh shenma[1-6] /etc/init.d/paramon restart

首先是要配置psvr节点的psvr文件
psvr文件一共有三个
cd /etc/paratera/
接下来修改pcnt的配置文件

也是修改三个文jian

